uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.identification

Class AdductDetector

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.identification.AdductDetector

  • public class AdductDetector
extends java.lang.Object
    Class implementing an adduct search method for a list of peaks. The input file containing adduct information must follow the following format:

    # comment line (x times) 1.008,Hydrogen ... ...

    One or many comment lines followed by lines containing the major isotopic mass and its label in comma-separated format. The adduct masses are corrected according to the specified ion mode.
